org.processmining.plugins.ilpminer

Class ILPModelJavaILP

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.processmining.plugins.ilpminer.ILPModelJavaILP
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PetriNetILPModel, PetriNetSingleILPModel

    public abstract class ILPModelJavaILP
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class provides a model for the ILP problem. It can be overwritten for a specific ILP problem model.
    Author:
    T. van der Wiel
